      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"bad day\" though. it's everything. i look at them and i just feel like i'm poisoning their lives by being part of it. like i'm just this constant weight on their shoulders. i can see it in their eyes, they're better off when i'm not around making everything harder.",
